 * falk@cs.fau.de--2008-systemoc-intern/SysteMoC--mainline--0.8--patch-108
   
 * Merge from SysteMoC--devel--0.8
 - Eliminated push_interface, can be implemented by add_interfaces directly
 - Changed visibility level of bind(sc_interface &) and bind(smoc_sysc_port &)
   to protected like equivalent functionallity in SystemC
 - Add public visible bind(<concrete interface> &) and
   bind(<concrete port type> &) to smoc_port_base<IFACE>
